POSIX-Account-ManageLDAP version 0.01
=====================================

POSIX::Account::ManageLDAP is used to manage LDAP server which use POSIX account as authetication account. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

     Net::LDAP
     Config::Simple
     Log::Dispatch

